We reserve the right, at any time, to change any fees or charges for Users (or to begin charging fees for any free service), provided that such changes will not apply to fees or charges paid prior to the time of the change. We will charge you sales tax as applicable to the Services or any order placed through the Services, based on your billing address. In addition, you will be responsible for all other taxes, levies, duties, or similar charges, only excluding taxes based on our income.
6. Changes to the Services
We reserve the right, at any time, to make changes to the Services. Such changes made include alterations to the features and functionality of the Websites and Apps, suspending or canceling certain portions of the Services offered, or limiting the Services that particular individuals or groups of individuals may access. Any change is made at the sole discretion of VoiceThread, except regarding changes to how Education Records are used or shared under these Terms and Conditions. VoiceThread will not make changes to the use of Education Records (as defined in the
Privacy Notice
